profile_positions.description:
The main purpose of Azerbaijan Netherlands Business Hub is to enhance economic cooperation between the Republic of Azerbaijan and the Kingdom of the Netherlands. 
We have an extensive business, political and educational network in both countries. Since the establishment many different activities are organized to connect both countries and to generate business. Several projects with common interests are developed. Our team of professionals is dedicated to serve both countries. 

Our offices are situated in Baku (AZ) and Venlo (NL).

Azerbaijan Netherlands Business Hub:
•	Operates as a bridge head for companies from both countries;
•	Organizes tailor made trade missions and business travel incentives;
•	Develops individual and joint projects;
•	Does project management and consultancy;
•	Connects companies by organizing visiting programs, business lunches and networking events;
•	Conducts market research; and
•	Is always ready to discuss business opportunities.

Do you want to know more what we can do together? Do not hesitate to contact us!
More info about our activities: www.aznlhub.com
